Story: CheckValue (function)
Given:
  x: Integer
  output: Text = ""

Step 1 → If x > 5
  Then: output becomes "large"
  Otherwise: output becomes "small"

End: Return output

---

Story: Test Function If/Otherwise

Given:
  x: Integer = 0
  result: Text = ""

Step 1 → Set x to 3
  Then: x becomes 3
  Then: result becomes CheckValue(x)
  
Step 2 → Show first result
  Effect: Show result
  
Step 3 → Set x to 10
  Then: x becomes 10
  Then: result becomes CheckValue(x)

Step 4 → Show second result
  Effect: Show result

End: Done
